    # pc "My mom and dad were sitting nearby. Dad had his arms wrapped around her and she was kind of nuzzling her head against his arm."
    pc "Meine Mama und mein Papa saßen in der Nähe. Papa hatte seine Arme um sie gelegt und sie schmiegte ihren Kopf irgendwie an seinen Arm."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba12.rpy:149
